    "body": "I have this issue as well at the same version. I believe `eth_getTransactionByHash` is using block_reader.go for `TxnLookup()` rather than eth_backend.go. IIRC block_reader should only be used during sync and not during up-to-date execution. Lookups are failing because its looking through the blocks db which pending txs do not exist in.",
